<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">04</div>
    <h2>函数</h2>
    <span class="tag">第2章 &middot; 第4节</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x2699;&#xFE0F;</span> 函数基础</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>定义：<code>def 函数名(参数列表):</code></li>
        <li>形参（定义时）vs 实参（调用时）</li>
        <li>返回值：<code>return</code> 可返回多个值（元组解包）</li>
        <li>说明文档：Docstring，用 <code>help()</code> 查看</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">circle_area</span>(r):
    <span class="string">"""根据半径计算圆的面积"""</span>
    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">3.14</span> * r * r

<span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="func">circle_area</span>(<span class="number">10</span>))  <span class="comment"># 314.0</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F504;</span> 进阶特性 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>嵌套调用：函数中调用其他函数，遵循栈结构 (LIFO)</li>
        <li>变量作用域：局部变量 vs 全局变量</li>
        <li><code>global</code> 关键字：在函数内修改全局变量</li>
        <li><code>nonlocal</code> 关键字：在嵌套函数中修改外层变量</li>
        <li><code>lambda</code> 匿名函数：<code>lambda 参数: 表达式</code></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># lambda 匿名函数</span>
add = <span class="keyword">lambda</span> a, b: a + b
<span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="func">add</span>(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">5</span>))  <span class="comment"># 8</span>

<span class="comment"># 常用于排序 key 参数</span>
students = [(<span class="string">"Alice"</span>, <span class="number">90</span>), (<span class="string">"Bob"</span>, <span class="number">85</span>)]
students.<span class="func">sort</span>(key=<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: x[<span class="number">1</span>], reverse=<span class="keyword">True</span>)
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F4E6;</span> 可变参数 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><code>*args</code>：接收任意数量的位置参数，打包为元组</li>
        <li><code>**kwargs</code>：接收任意数量的关键字参数，打包为字典</li>
        <li>参数顺序：普通参数 &rarr; *args &rarr; 关键字参数 &rarr; **kwargs</li>
        <li><code>*</code> 可解包列表/元组为位置参数</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">total</span>(*args, **kwargs):
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">f"位置参数: {args}"</span>)    <span class="comment"># (1, 2, 3)</span>
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">f"关键字参数: {kwargs}"</span>)  <span class="comment"># {'tax': 0.1}</span>

<span class="func">total</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, tax=<span class="number">0.1</span>)

<span class="comment"># 解包调用</span>
nums = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]
<span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="func">max</span>(*nums))  <span class="comment"># 等价 max(1, 2, 3)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F3C6;</span> 装饰器 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>本质：一个接收函数并返回函数的高阶函数</li>
        <li>语法糖：<code>@装饰器名</code> 写在函数定义上方</li>
        <li>执行顺序：从下到上、从外到内</li>
        <li><code>functools.wraps</code> 保留被装饰函数的元信息</li>
        <li>常用于：日志记录、权限校验、性能计时、缓存</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">import</span> time
<span class="keyword">from</span> functools <span class="keyword">import</span> wraps

<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">timer</span>(func):
    @wraps(func)
    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">wrapper</span>(*args, **kwargs):
        start = time.time()
        result = <span class="func">func</span>(*args, **kwargs)
        <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">f"{func.__name__} 耗时 {time.time()-start:.2f}s"</span>)
        <span class="keyword">return</span> result
    <span class="keyword">return</span> wrapper

@timer
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">slow_func</span>():
    time.sleep(<span class="number">1</span>)
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mnemonic">
    <div class="mnemonic-title"><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 记忆口诀 &amp; 白话解读</div>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 函数 = "菜谱"</strong> &mdash; 函数是写好的菜谱，def 是菜名，参数是食材，return 是出锅的菜。你不用每次从头做，照着菜谱（调用函数）来就行。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; *args / **kwargs 的区别：</strong>*args 是你随便往袋子里塞东西（位置参数，打包成元组），**kwargs 是你贴了标签往袋子里塞（关键字参数，打包成字典）。记忆法：一个星*装"散装货"，两个星**装"带标签的"。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 装饰器 = "手机壳"</strong> &mdash; 你的手机（原函数）功能不变，但套上不同的手机壳（装饰器）就有了新功能：防摔、变好看、加支架……套一层不够还能套多层，从外到里依次生效。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 作用域口诀：</strong>"内能读外，外不能读内" &mdash; 函数内部能用外面的变量，但函数外面看不到里面的。想在内部改外面的变量？用 <code>global</code>（全局）或 <code>nonlocal</code>（外层函数）。</p>
  </div>
</div>

