<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">07</div>
    <h2>文件操作</h2>
    <span class="tag">第2章 &middot; 第7节</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F4C2;</span> 文件读写 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><code>open(文件路径, 模式, encoding)</code> 打开文件</li>
        <li><code>with</code> 上下文管理器：自动关闭文件，推荐用法</li>
        <li>模式：<code>r</code> 读 / <code>w</code> 写（覆盖） / <code>a</code> 追加 / <code>rb/wb</code> 二进制</li>
        <li>读取：<code>read()</code> 全部 / <code>readline()</code> 逐行 / <code>readlines()</code> 行列表</li>
        <li>写入：<code>write()</code> 写字符串 / <code>writelines()</code> 写列表</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 读取文件</span>
<span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="func">open</span>(<span class="string">"data.txt"</span>, <span class="string">"r"</span>, encoding=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:
    content = f.<span class="func">read</span>()       <span class="comment"># 读全部</span>
    lines = f.<span class="func">readlines</span>()   <span class="comment"># 读所有行</span>

<span class="comment"># 写入文件</span>
<span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="func">open</span>(<span class="string">"output.txt"</span>, <span class="string">"w"</span>, encoding=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:
    f.<span class="func">write</span>(<span class="string">"Hello, Python!\n"</span>)

<span class="comment"># 逐行遍历（内存友好）</span>
<span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="func">open</span>(<span class="string">"data.txt"</span>, <span class="string">"r"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:
    <span class="keyword">for</span> line <span class="keyword">in</span> f:
        <span class="keyword">print</span>(line.<span class="func">strip</span>())
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F4BE;</span> CSV 与 JSON</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>CSV：<code>csv.reader()</code> 读 / <code>csv.writer()</code> 写</li>
        <li>JSON：<code>json.load()</code> 读 / <code>json.dump()</code> 写</li>
        <li>JSON 是 API 数据交换的通用格式</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">import</span> json, csv

<span class="comment"># JSON 读写</span>
data = {<span class="string">"name"</span>: <span class="string">"Python"</span>, <span class="string">"ver"</span>: <span class="number">3.12</span>}
<span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="func">open</span>(<span class="string">"data.json"</span>, <span class="string">"w"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:
    json.<span class="func">dump</span>(data, f, ensure_ascii=<span class="keyword">False</span>, indent=<span class="number">2</span>)

<span class="comment"># CSV 读取</span>
<span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="func">open</span>(<span class="string">"scores.csv"</span>, <span class="string">"r"</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:
    reader = csv.<span class="func">DictReader</span>(f)
    <span class="keyword">for</span> row <span class="keyword">in</span> reader:
        <span class="keyword">print</span>(row[<span class="string">"name"</span>], row[<span class="string">"score"</span>])
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mnemonic">
    <div class="mnemonic-title"><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 记忆口诀 &amp; 白话解读</div>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; <code>with open()</code> = "用完自动关门"</strong> &mdash; 就像进酒店房间，<code>with</code> 就是房卡，进去之后门自动上锁，出来自动解锁。你不用操心关文件，Python 帮你搞定。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 三种模式一句话：</strong>"r 读、w 写、a 追加"。r 是翻开书看，w 是拿笔重写整页（原来的内容没了！），a 是在末尾接着写（原来的内容还在）。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 逐行读取最省内存</strong> &mdash; <code>for line in f</code> 就像吃饭一口一口吃，而不是把整桌菜一口气塞嘴里。处理大文件时，这种方式不会撑爆内存。</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===================== 第8节 ===================== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">08</div>
    <h2>异常处理</h2>
    <span class="tag">第2章 &middot; 第8节</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F6A8;</span> try...except</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><code>try</code>：可能出错的代码</li>
        <li><code>except 异常类型 as e</code>：捕获并处理异常</li>
        <li><code>else</code>：无异常时执行</li>
        <li><code>finally</code>：无论是否异常都执行（资源清理）</li>
        <li>捕获具体异常优于捕获 <code>Exception</code></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">try</span>:
    num = <span class="func">int</span>(<span class="func">input</span>(<span class="string">"请输入数字: "</span>))
    result = <span class="number">100</span> / num
<span class="keyword">except</span> <span class="func">ValueError</span>:
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">"输入的不是数字"</span>)
<span class="keyword">except</span> <span class="func">ZeroDivisionError</span>:
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">"不能除以零"</span>)
<span class="keyword">else</span>:
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">f"结果: {result}"</span>)
<span class="keyword">finally</span>:
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="string">"程序结束"</span>)
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 常见异常</h3>
      <table class="summary-table">
        <tr><th>异常</th><th>说明</th></tr>
        <tr><td><code>TypeError</code></td><td>类型错误，如对 str 做数学运算</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>ValueError</code></td><td>值错误，如 <code>int("abc")</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>IndexError</code></td><td>索引越界</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>KeyError</code></td><td>字典键不存在</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>FileNotFoundError</code></td><td>文件不存在</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>ZeroDivisionError</code></td><td>除以零</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>AttributeError</code></td><td>对象没有该属性</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F6AB;</span> 异常抛出与自定义</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><code>raise 异常类型("消息")</code>：主动抛出异常</li>
        <li>自定义异常：继承 <code>Exception</code> 类</li>
        <li>异常链：<code>raise ... from 原异常</code></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="func">AgeError</span>(Exception):
    <span class="keyword">pass</span>

<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">set_age</span>(age):
    <span class="keyword">if</span> age < <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> age > <span class="number">150</span>:
        <span class="keyword">raise</span> <span class="func">AgeError</span>(<span class="string">f"年龄 {age} 不合法"</span>)
    <span class="keyword">return</span> age
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mnemonic">
    <div class="mnemonic-title"><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 记忆口诀 &amp; 白话解读</div>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; try...except = "安全气囊"</strong> &mdash; 开车（运行代码）时不一定出事，但万一撞了（报错），安全气囊（except）能保你一命。别怕写可能出错的代码，套上 try 就有保障。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 四兄弟分工：</strong>try = "试试看"，except = "出事了我来处理"，else = "没出事我来收尾"，finally = "不管出不出事我都得干"（比如关闭文件、释放资源）。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 异常继承关系：</strong>Exception 是"万能老爹"，ValueError、TypeError、FileNotFoundError 都是它的"儿子"。捕获具体异常就像"找对人办事"，比直接找老爹效率高。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; raise = "拉响警报"</strong> &mdash; 你发现数据不对，主动 raise 一个异常，就像发现火情拉响火警铃，让上面的人赶紧处理。</p>
  </div>
</div>

