<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">09</div>
    <h2>推导式与生成器</h2>
    <span class="tag">第2章 &middot; 第9节</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x26A1;</span> 推导式 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>列表推导式</strong>：<code>[expr for x in iterable if condition]</code></li>
        <li><strong>字典推导式</strong>：<code>{k: v for k, v in iterable}</code></li>
        <li><strong>集合推导式</strong>：<code>{expr for x in iterable}</code></li>
        <li>替代 <code>map()</code> / <code>filter()</code>，更 Pythonic</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 列表推导式</span>
squares = [x**<span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">11</span>)]
even = [x <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">21</span>) <span class="keyword">if</span> x % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span>]

<span class="comment"># 字典推导式</span>
scores = {<span class="string">"Alice"</span>: <span class="number">90</span>, <span class="string">"Bob"</span>: <span class="number">85</span>, <span class="string">"Charlie"</span>: <span class="number">92</span>}
passed = {k: v <span class="keyword">for</span> k, v <span class="keyword">in</span> scores.<span class="func">items</span>() <span class="keyword">if</span> v >= <span class="number">90</span>}
<span class="comment"># {'Alice': 90, 'Charlie': 92}</span>

<span class="comment"># 嵌套推导式</span>
matrix = [[i*j <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>)] <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>)]
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F331;</span> 生成器 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>生成器函数：用 <code>yield</code> 替代 <code>return</code></li>
        <li>惰性求值：每次 <code>next()</code> 只产出一个值，节省内存</li>
        <li>生成器表达式：<code>(expr for x in iterable)</code>（圆括号）</li>
        <li>常用于：大数据流处理、无限序列、管道式处理</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 生成器函数</span>
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">countdown</span>(n):
    <span class="keyword">while</span> n > <span class="number">0</span>:
        <span class="keyword">yield</span> n
        n -= <span class="number">1</span>

<span class="keyword">for</span> num <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">countdown</span>(<span class="number">5</span>):
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(num, end=<span class="string">" "</span>)  <span class="comment"># 5 4 3 2 1</span>

<span class="comment"># 生成器表达式（节省内存）</span>
big_sum = <span class="func">sum</span>(x**<span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> x <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">range</span>(<span class="number">10_000_000</span>))
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F9E9;</span> 迭代器协议 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>可迭代对象：实现了 <code>__iter__()</code> 方法的对象</li>
        <li>迭代器：实现了 <code>__iter__()</code> 和 <code>__next__()</code></li>
        <li><code>iter()</code> 获取迭代器，<code>next()</code> 获取下一个元素</li>
        <li><code>StopIteration</code>：迭代结束时抛出</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="func">Countdown</span>:
    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">__init__</span>(self, start):
        self.current = start

    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">__iter__</span>(self):
        <span class="keyword">return</span> self

    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">__next__</span>(self):
        <span class="keyword">if</span> self.current <= <span class="number">0</span>:
            <span class="keyword">raise</span> <span class="func">StopIteration</span>
        val = self.current
        self.current -= <span class="number">1</span>
        <span class="keyword">return</span> val

<span class="keyword">for</span> n <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="func">Countdown</span>(<span class="number">3</span>):
    <span class="keyword">print</span>(n, end=<span class="string">" "</span>)  <span class="comment"># 3 2 1</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mnemonic">
    <div class="mnemonic-title"><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 记忆口诀 &amp; 白话解读</div>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 推导式 = "一行搞定循环"</strong> &mdash; 普通写法要 3-4 行的 for 循环 + if 判断，推导式一行写完。就像速溶咖啡 vs 手冲咖啡：结果差不多，但推导式快得多。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 推导式三兄弟：</strong>[ ] 列表推导、{ } 字典推导、{ } 集合推导。口诀：方括号变列表，花括号看有没有冒号 &mdash; 有冒号是字典，没冒号是集合。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; yield = "暂停键"</strong> &mdash; 普通函数 return 是"把菜全做好端出来"，yield 是"做一道上一道，顾客吃着我接着做"。每次 yield 暂停，下次从暂停的地方继续，所以不吃内存。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 生成器 vs 列表：</strong>列表是一次性把所有数据放进内存（自助餐全摆出来），生成器是用多少生成多少（点菜模式做一道上一道）。数据量大时用生成器，省内存。</p>
  </div>
</div>

