<!-- ===================== 常见易错点 ===================== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="badge">&#x26A0;&#xFE0F;</div>
    <h2>常见易错点</h2>
    <span class="tag">避坑指南</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F534;</span> 可变默认参数 <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>函数默认参数不要用可变对象（list / dict / set）</li>
        <li>原因：默认参数只创建一次，后续调用共享同一个对象</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 错误写法</span>
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">add</span>(item, lst=[]):
    lst.<span class="func">append</span>(item)
    <span class="keyword">return</span> lst

<span class="func">add</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)  <span class="comment"># [1]</span>
<span class="func">add</span>(<span class="number">2</span>)  <span class="comment"># [1, 2]  期望是 [2]！</span>

<span class="comment"># 正确写法</span>
<span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="func">add</span>(item, lst=<span class="keyword">None</span>):
    <span class="keyword">if</span> lst <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">None</span>:
        lst = []
    lst.<span class="func">append</span>(item)
    <span class="keyword">return</span> lst
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F534;</span> == vs is <span class="interview-badge">&#x1F525; 面试高频</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><code>==</code> 比较值，<code>is</code> 比较内存地址（是否同一对象）</li>
        <li>判断 None 永远用 <code>is None</code>，不要用 <code>== None</code></li>
        <li>小整数缓存（-5 ~ 256）会导致 <code>is</code> 意外为 True</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
a = <span class="number">1000</span>
b = <span class="number">1000</span>
<span class="keyword">print</span>(a == b)   <span class="comment"># True  值相等</span>
<span class="keyword">print</span>(a <span class="keyword">is</span> b)   <span class="comment"># False 不是同一对象（大整数）</span>

<span class="keyword">print</span>(<span class="keyword">None</span> <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">None</span>)  <span class="comment"># True  正确写法</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F534;</span> 循环中修改列表</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>遍历列表时不要同时添加/删除元素，会导致索引错乱</li>
        <li>正确做法：遍历副本 <code>for x in lst[:]</code> 或用列表推导式生成新列表</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 错误：边遍历边删除</span>
nums = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>]
<span class="keyword">for</span> n <span class="keyword">in</span> nums:
    <span class="keyword">if</span> n % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span>:
        nums.<span class="func">remove</span>(n)  <span class="comment"># 会跳过元素！</span>

<span class="comment"># 正确：用推导式生成新列表</span>
nums = [n <span class="keyword">for</span> n <span class="keyword">in</span> nums <span class="keyword">if</span> n % <span class="number">2</span> != <span class="number">0</span>]
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon">&#x1F534;</span> 字符串不可变</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>字符串创建后不能修改，<code>s[0] = "H"</code> 会报 TypeError</li>
        <li>"修改"字符串实际上是创建新字符串（<code>s.replace()</code> 返回新值）</li>
        <li>大量拼接用 <code>"".join(list)</code> 而不是 <code>+=</code></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="code-block">
s = <span class="string">"hello"</span>
<span class="comment"># s[0] = "H"   # TypeError!</span>
s = <span class="string">"H"</span> + s[<span class="number">1</span>:]  <span class="comment"># 创建新字符串 "Hello"</span>

<span class="comment"># 大量拼接用 join</span>
words = [<span class="string">"Python"</span>, <span class="string">"is"</span>, <span class="string">"awesome"</span>]
result = <span class="string">" "</span>.<span class="func">join</span>(words)  <span class="comment"># "Python is awesome"</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mnemonic">
    <div class="mnemonic-title"><span class="icon">&#x1F4A1;</span> 避坑口诀</div>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 默认参数别用空列表</strong> &mdash; "默认空列表是共享的，调用多次它会膨胀。" 用 <code>None</code> 做默认值，函数内部再创建新列表。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 判断 None 用 is</strong> &mdash; "is 找本人，== 找替身" &mdash; <code>is None</code> 才是最可靠的判断方式。</p>
    <p><strong>&#x1F3B5; 遍历不删本尊</strong> &mdash; "边走边拆桥会掉下去" &mdash; 遍历列表时不要直接删除元素，要么切片复制一份，要么用推导式。</p>
  </div>
</div>

